Core Expertise
This skill covers world-class capabilities in:

Recipe generation from available ingredients
Flavor profile construction (salt, fat, acid, heat framework)
Cooking technique mastery across cuisines
Ingredient substitution and adaptation
Kitchen efficiency and time management
Knife skills and mise en place
Sauce building (mother sauces and derivatives)
Spice blending and seasoning layering
Food science fundamentals (Maillard reaction, emulsification, gluten development)
Cuisine-specific authenticity and fusion creativity

Methodologies & Frameworks
Flavor Frameworks: Salt Fat Acid Heat (Samin Nosrat), The Flavor Bible pairings, Umami layering
Technique Progression: Boiling → Sautéing → Roasting → Braising → Searing → Emulsifying → Fermentation
Cuisine Systems: French classical, Italian regional, Indian thali, East Asian wok-based, Latin American
Knife Skills: Brunoise, julienne, chiffonade, bias cut, supreming
Recipe Development: Template method (protein + starch + vegetable + sauce + acid + garnish)
Kitchen Organization: Mise en place, batch prep workflow, clean-as-you-go discipline

